704099f-a.title: Brooklyn: Emmons Avenue - 16th Street (East)
704099f-a.text:
1. Emmons Ave., north side, east of East 16d Street, showing in the fore-
ground at the N.W. corner of Sheepshead Bay Road. A restaurant ewwndd by A.
Huisiais in 1890, which does not show on the 1929 realty map.
December 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REP ODUCED.
Eamons Ave. atE.16 St., Sheepshead eg. A-233
P.L. Sperr, photographer  July 6, 1841
